title: After the Storm
description: In this Dateline classic, when a beautiful woman is strangled to death in her Texas home, police look at the men in the victim’s life, while also considering that a stranger may have killed her. Keith Morrison reports. Originally aired on NBC on September 23, 2016.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
